						 <p>I thought it was good, upvoted. I think my favorite is the blue one.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Here&nbsp;are&nbsp;a&nbsp;few&nbsp;comments&nbsp;that&nbsp;I&nbsp;think&nbsp;might&nbsp;improve&nbsp;clarity.</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Here&nbsp;are&nbsp;a&nbsp;few&nbsp;comments&nbsp;that&nbsp;I&nbsp;think&nbsp;might&nbsp;improve&nbsp;clarity.</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>The description says the skeletons are identical, but their overall shape is the only thing identical, everything else is different.<br /> &quot;Television program&quot; might fit a clinical tone better than &quot;TV show.&quot;<br /> &quot;At the warehouse in which SCP-2263 was recovered a mattress&#8230;&quot; I am pretty sure there should be a semicolon after recovered.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
